name: Cabbage Patch Kids: The Patch Puppy Rescue
name_original: Cabbage Patch Kids: The Patch Puppy Rescue
description:
Cabbage Patch Kids: The Patch Puppy Rescue is an arcade game developed by 1st Playable Productions. It was originally released in 2006. It was published by D3 Publisher.
You can play Cabbage Patch Kids: The Patch Puppy Rescue on Game Boy Advance.
